Package: aire.zmvm
Type: Package
Title: Download pollution data for the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:  c(person("Diego", "Valle-Jones", email = "diego@diegovalle.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package can download the daily maximum, minimum, or hourly average for each
    of the pollution measuring stations or geographic zones in the Mexico City Metro Area.
    It also contains the locations of each of the stations.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    ggplot2,
    seasonal,
    viridis,
    gstat,
    sp,
    ggmap
Imports:
    data.table,
    lubridate,
    dplyr,
    rvest,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    xml2,
    httr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
